com.phonegap.calendar.android.model
Class Who

java.lang.Object
  com.phonegap.calendar.android.model.Who

public class Who
extends java.lang.Object

A person associated with the containing entity. The type of the association is determined by the rel attribute; the details about the person are contained in an embedded or linked-to Contact entry.

The Who element can be used to specify email senders and recipients, calendar event organizers, and so on.

Author:
Alain Vongsouvanh, Nicolas Garnier, Sergio Martinez Rodriguez

email

public java.lang.String email
Email address. This property is typically used when EntryLink is not specified. The address must comply with RFC 2822, section 3.4.1.

attendeeStatus

public AttendeeStatus attendeeStatus
